    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in showroom condition. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, glass-like luster, free from any rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating and has resided exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Step inside to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and the cabin still retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature and electronic sensor functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, paper-documented service history from authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather-only vehicle. Included in the sale are all original owner\u2019s manuals, both sets of master keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks and performs just as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
